            d="M7 2h10a5 5 0 015 5v10a5 5 0 01-5 5H7a5 5 0 01-5-5V7a5 5 0 015-5zm0 2a3 3 0 00-3 3v10a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3V7a3 3 0 00-3-3H7zm5 3.5a5.5 5.5 0 110 11 5.5 5.5 0 010-11zm0 2a3.5 3.5 0 100 7 3.5 3.5 0 000-7zM17.5 6a1.5 1.5 0 110 3 1.5 1.5 0 010-3z"
          ></path>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
